    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台商家套利细则》、《京东开放平台商家违规管理总则》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1255847210776662016",
    "content": "<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 您好，为适应业务发展需求，将修订《京东开放平台商家套利细则》、《京东开放平台商家违规管理总则》，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年6月30日- </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">2025年7月6日，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; color: #000000;\">规则预计于2025年7月7日生效，</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> </span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">核心调整点：<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-size: 10pt;\"> 调整商家套利违规场景定义及处理措施。</span></span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">原规则链接：①商家套利：<a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=760061764627992576&amp;type=0\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=760061764627992576&amp;type=0</a>；②违规总则：<a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2754&amp;btype=1\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2754&amp;btype=1</a></span></span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">修订内容如下：</span></span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\">\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 100.0%; border-collapse: collapse;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 14.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 32.22%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"32%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">对应规则</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.72%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"33%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订前</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 34.06%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-left: none; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 14.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"34%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">修订后</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 198.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 32.22%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 198.0pt;\" rowspan=\"2\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"32%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">《京东开放平台商家套利细则》</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 198.0pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"33%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">【违规定义】<br />1.1商家套利：指商家不遵守诚信原则，实施谋私舞弊、虚假操作、套利或套垫付款行为（包括但不限于套取京东款项、京东优惠券、京豆、红包、佣金、垫付款及/或其他京东经营资源等）或实施其他侵害京东、客户、平台其他商家利益的行为。本规则所称商家，包括商家加盟门店等关联机构；商家应保证其关联机构同样遵守平台规则的约定，商家对其关联机构的行为造成的一切后果承担连带保证责任。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 34.06%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 198.0pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"34%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">【违规定义】<br />1.1商家套利：指商家不遵守诚信原则，实施谋私舞弊、虚假操作、套利或套垫付款行为（包括但不限于套取京东款项、京东优惠券、</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: red;\">促销</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、京豆、红包、佣金、垫付款及/或其他京东经营资源等）或实施其他侵害京东、客户、平台其他商家利益的行为。本规则所称商家，包括商家加盟门店等关联机构；商家应保证其关联机构同样遵守平台规则的约定，商家对其关联机构的行为造成的一切后果承担连带保证责任。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 181.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 33.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 181.5pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"33%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.5</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">除上述处理措施外，京东有权视违规程度追缴套利或套垫付款款项、延迟结算、关闭/停用价保等权益、关闭/停用工具、商品下架、全店限售、钱包冻结、限制服务市场交易、永久限制参与各类型营销优惠、限制同主体下店铺使用营销优惠、关闭违规商家店铺，商家应向京东赔偿全部损失，除此之外还应支付违约金壹佰万元或按所涉商品销售额2倍支付违约金，二者从高适用。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 34.06%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 181.5pt;\" width=\"34%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.5</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">除上述处理措施外，京东有权视违规程度追缴套利或套垫付款款项、延迟结算、关闭/停用价保等权益、关闭/停用工具、商品下架、全店限售、延迟结算、钱包冻结、</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: red;\">暂停分账</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、限制服务市场交易、</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: red;\">门店置休、门店下线</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、永久限制参与各类型营销优惠、限制同主体下店铺使用营销优惠、关闭违规商家店铺，商家应向京东赔偿全部损失，除此之外还应支付违约金壹佰万元或按所涉商品销售额2倍支付违约金，二者从高适用。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 330.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 32.22%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 330.0pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"32%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; text-align: center;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">《京东开放平台商家违规管理总则》</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.72%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 330.0pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"33%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">22</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【商家套利】<br /><br />商家不遵守诚信原则，实施谋私舞弊、虚假操作、套利或套垫付款行为（包括但不限于套取京东款项、京东优惠券、京豆、红包、佣金、垫付款及/或其他京东经营资源等）或实施其他侵害京东、客户、平台其他商家利益的行为。京东有权视违规程度采取包括但不限于扣除违约金、延迟结算、剔除商家优惠券、京豆、红包使用资格、关闭/停用价保等权益、关闭/停用工具、商品下架、全店限售、钱包冻结、限制服务市场交易、店铺清退等处理措施。同时，京东有权追缴套券套利款项。本规则所称商家，包括商家加盟门店等关联机构；商家应保证其关联机构同样遵守平台规则的约定，商家对其关联机构的行为造成的一切后果承担连带保证责任。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 34.06%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 330.0pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"34%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">22</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【商家套利】<br /><br />商家不遵守诚信原则，实施谋私舞弊、虚假操作、套利或套垫付款行为（包括但不限于套取京东款项、京东优惠券、</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: red;\">促销</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、京豆、红包、佣金、垫付款及/或其他京东经营资源等）或实施其他侵害京东、客户、平台其他商家利益的行为。京东有权视违规程度采取包括但不限于扣除违约金、延迟结算、剔除商家优惠券、</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: red;\">促销</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、京豆、红包使用资格、关闭/停用价保等权益、关闭/停用工具、商品下架、全店限售、延迟结算、钱包冻结、暂停分账、限制服务市场交易、</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: red;\">门店置休、门店下线</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、店铺清退等处理措施。同时，京东有权追缴套券套利款项。本规则所称商家，包括商家加盟门店等关联机构；商家应保证其关联机构同样遵守平台规则的约定，商家对其关联机构的行为造成的一切后果承担连带保证责任。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\">&nbsp;</div>",
